plot: Series revolves around six teens and the staff at Wellness Canyon, a weight-loss camp. It centers on Will, a funny, opinionated overweight girl sent to the camp by her wealthy parents who own a chain of fitness centers, and Amber, a curvy teen who is the skinniest and hottest girl at the camp but who considers herself too heavy.   Written by  Anonymous
